      <title>电动汽车制造商 Lion Electric 现金短缺，接近债权人最后期限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/ev-maker-lion-electric-nears-creditor-deadline-as-cash-dwindles</link>
